data.description: Excellent opportunity to own this cozy two-story 4 bed-3.5 bath single family home in the community of Encore in West Kendall. This property features tile flooring through living, dinning area and kitchen, wood and laminate floor in bedrooms (2nd floor), tiled bathrooms, kitchen with wooden cabinetry, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, water heater (2018), laundry room with washer & dryer hook up. Impact windows and doors were installed in the 1st floor. The 4th bedroom is a converted garage. The roof was replaced in 2019. A/C 2020. Located in a great neighborhood minutes away from local shops, gas stations and great schools. Well kept backyard, ideal for gatherings. Community pool and tennis court. Enjoy everything this home has to offer!
